Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You've found a job as a waitress and a place to live,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.55,0:00:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but this bed is pretty horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how much it tilts when I sit on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.97,0:00:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd try to sleep on it, it'd easily fall over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sleep on the bed. You should sleep on that sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't sleep there either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.35,0:00:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to Dr. Reichwine's place in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because you have to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.07,0:00:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're not going to study at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You can teach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Studying isn't enough. At this rate\Nyou won't have any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I have friends. You and Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I wasn't around, you'd be the one who's lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.38,0:00:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, you're going back to Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.47,0:00:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.76,0:00:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Nina! Are you going today, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.31,0:01:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.19,0:01:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Give it up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You go to the same place every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times you do it, it's always the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We lived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:53.90,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)\pos(360,340)}The Door to Memories
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom and myself... and Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, Johan was dragged down these stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina is my name now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I called back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina? Anna?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My name...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The car that Johan was in drove along this road.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't hide anything from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The children gathered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They listened to what was called a reading seminar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,At this Red Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The lock is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They tried to make them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The superior students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are the superior students?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:04:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He ran on foot and escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He ran through the rose bushes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I waited in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I waited for Mom to come home...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,for Johan to come home...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,while reading this picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans can become anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,While they were holding reading seminars\Nat the Red Rose Mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in this room reading this book,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and waiting for Johan to come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I was smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I faced the opening door and said
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Welcome home."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home. Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home. Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home. Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home. Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home. Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But the door wouldn't open.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times I said, "Welcome\Nhome," the door wouldn't open.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't open! It wouldn't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't remember anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the same. I have a lot of painful memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I'll go to Dr. Reichwine's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too. You're coming home with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do what Tenma told us to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on... happy memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,let's make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:26.09,Names2,,0,0,40,,{\fad(500,0)\an8}Prague Police Station\N(Czech Republic)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait a minute, Officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, all I can do is\Nsit next to the officer and listen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We plan to fulfill your request to the fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The fullest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in the best case scenario, I can only\Nspend 30 minutes with each of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Just listening to them should be good enough for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an exception of exceptions to cooperate\Nwith you this much already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a miracle if we can prepare the 5 witnesses for testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:08:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we have to use this chance to\Ncollect as many testimonies as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.74,0:08:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They probably wouldn't want to talk about their own past...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.33,0:08:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The children from the reading seminars...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.75,0:08:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All the skeletons that they just found
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,must have something to do with the former\NCzechoslovakian secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth, in this case, might just stay in the bushes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the head detective in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mr. Verdeman, a lawyer from Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Detective Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already arranged a list of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do everything exactly as I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only here as an observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:09:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,3 Cerveny Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.59,0:09:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A.k.a. the Red Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It burned down and this is its current condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake that in '68,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you participated in a reading seminar there, Mr. Erno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know of the man called Franz Bonaparta?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you please be quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just trying to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to be so careful that you let\Nthis end without getting any information?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand how much\Nwe had to do just to set this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that the mansion was a positive force in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, looking at the burned remains\Nof the mansion, how do I put it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that sadness would bubble to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't feel homesick or anything like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Homesick?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That was like school to you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:10:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Verdeman! Please be quiet. I can't\Nask the questions that I've prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadness... Homesickness...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Emotional scars?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think participating in the reading\Nseminars has had an effect on your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a family?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to answer. You have that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't really a problem with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Our kids, my eldest son and his little\Nbrother, committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't really have problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.24,0:10:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did they commit suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that your questions\Nstick too much to the manual.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what have we learned so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just like a kid these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably hit on women using a manual.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You look just like a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a father, but I'd never want a parent like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The next person may come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My memories of the reading seminars?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything you can tell us. No matter how small.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"The God of Peace is very busy."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"He doesn't have time to look in the mirror.\NHe blows his trumpet every day."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The God of Peace by Klaus Poppe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You know of this, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I kind of remember it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I also like the one about the monster from\Nthe west and the monster from the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:12:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you like about these books?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I put it? They take me away to a different world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A different world?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Crying, being happy, being scared...\NAll those feelings just seem to go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does this book make you feel that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's true that I don't feel anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Even your own name disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That is true freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you feel that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Franz Bonaparta teach you to be that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that person? The person who read to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you remember clearly from the seminars?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What I remember clearly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, a man came to visit the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They said he was from a radio program.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:13:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He liked the song "Somewhere Over the Rainbow."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He told us about The Wizard of Oz.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.67,0:13:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you after?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like you're asking questions\Nfor your own personal information.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here for personal reasons, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the young detective who was framed for a\Nseries of incidents because of the secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's you, right, Detective Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You've become desperate to clear your own name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was arrested for being\Na spy for former East Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I always believed that my father was innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But my father really was a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe in anything anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, I'm trying to prove that a certain man is innocent,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm trying to find something to believe in again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The person whom the witness is talking about...\NThe man from the radio program...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,is my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My father might have been part of the brainwashing\Nexperiments at the Red Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I mustn't look away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,May I go home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The man I was talking about told me this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"Run away from here."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"There is a good place somewhere over the rainbow."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"That is where your family is."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dorothy from The Wizard of Oz was able to go home in the end."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"You should ran away from here, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I cut all my ties to the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife and kids are waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We mustn't avert our eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two more people to be interviewed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dieter. Stop daydreaming and hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be your desk for studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina doesn't want to talk about what happened in Prague.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,From what you told me, she probably\Nremembered a lot of her memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that the brakes were applied before\Nthe last bit of memory was recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.41,0:16:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I did something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You did a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put this desk together already so that\Nwe can have white sausage and beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You ate all the white sausage last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? What have I done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We brought your favorite, white sausage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so considerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Reichwine. How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I haven't gotten in touch with you for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.57,0:16:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.24,0:16:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to have made you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I m fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You know of Eva Heinemann, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She is currently being pursued by that organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've sent her to you. Please take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of Nina and Dieter, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In my mind, this is the only way to end this series of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,From Kenzo Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a letter I received three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been no sign that Eva is trying to get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where this was mailed from.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The stamp is hard to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you look it up, Karl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.21,0:17:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you could find out where Tenma is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,However, what concerns me is this last sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"In my mind, this is the only way\Nto end this series of events."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's finish putting that desk together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I still have my coordination after that beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Reichwine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to remember everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you prepared for when that happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to use any method to get my memory back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're serious about it, I don't want to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But, if that's what you really want...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am, Dr. Gillen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.94,0:18:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Except...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the things I talk about under hypnosis...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,might be extremely scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine. Let's face this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Close your eyes, take a deep breath,\Nand relax your whole body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Describe your mother for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.51,0:19:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom... Kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sing... Singing voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A beautiful singing voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of bean soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.99,0:19:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How about your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad was a government soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.83,0:19:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A government soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you meet him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom said Dad was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom was an anti-government activist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father was killed and your mother, who was involved in anti-government activities, fled the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:19:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was she running from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The three frogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But, my brother was caught...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,by the man with the glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother was caught...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.78,0:20:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Red Rose Mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people died!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what your brother saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.29,0:20:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The rose's thorns hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I know where Tenma's letter was mailed from.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You've remembered everything, haven't you, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.82,0:20:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:20:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. There's nothing to be afraid of. Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:20:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. There's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.09,0:21:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.72,0:21:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to clap my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When I do that you'll wake up from your hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.69,0:21:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I say something terrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.74,0:21:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But you remembered it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:52.62,Names2,,0,0,40,,{\fad(500,0)\an8}2 Days Later
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.59,0:21:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Reichwine, Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.97,0:22:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me for leaving so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.39,0:22:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to Frankfurt, where Tenma is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.57,0:22:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I know where Johan came from and where he will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.99,0:22:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If I go, I could end it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.58,0:22:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If I go, I could save Tenma.
