Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.89,0:22:39.50,ED3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Gazing at what is known
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:43.38,ED3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}now in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:59.86,ED3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Your eyes believe in kindness
